p: Jurkat cells (5 × 10 4 cells/mL) were treated with A.S. extract (0–30 μg/mL) and incubated for 24–72 h. Annexin V and 7-AAD levels were analyzed with the Dead Cell Assay Kit by the MUSE ® Cell Analyzer and MUSE ® Annexin V and Dead Cell software module (Merck Millipore). For the quantitative measurements of reactive oxygen species (ROS), the MUSE ® Oxidative Stress Kit was also used.
